sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  box rgb(238,229,247) Source sandbox
    participant SourceChamber as Source Chamber
  end
  box rgb(220,236,255) Source trusted host
    participant SourceCell as Source Cell
  end
  box rgb(255,242,204) Current authority
    participant Authority as Route and generation authority
  end
  box rgb(220,236,255) Target trusted host
    participant TargetCell as Target Cell
  end
  box rgb(238,229,247) Target sandbox
    participant TargetChamber as Target Chamber
  end

  SourceChamber->>SourceCell: Delegate exact primitive execution
  SourceCell->>Authority: Resolve current projected route member
  Authority-->>SourceCell: Member, assignment, source image and route epoch
  alt Local member
    SourceCell->>TargetChamber: Validated local ingress
    TargetChamber-->>SourceCell: Normalized outcome
  else Remote current member
    SourceCell->>TargetCell: TLS 1.3 signed execution envelope
    TargetCell->>Authority: Verify enrollment and exact current generation
    Authority-->>TargetCell: Current authority agrees
    TargetCell->>TargetChamber: Proceed with exact ingress
    TargetChamber-->>TargetCell: Normalized outcome
    TargetCell-->>SourceCell: Signed result preserving started state
  else Stale or unauthorized member
    Authority-->>SourceCell: Generation, epoch or assignment mismatch
    SourceCell--xSourceChamber: Reject before target affect and do not reroute silently
  end
  SourceCell-->>SourceChamber: Continue graph with result or explicit failure
